# KeePass
# https://faq.i3wm.org/question/2067/focus-on-a-window-of-a-certain-class-unless-it-has-a-certain-title/?answer=2068#post-id-2068
for_window [title="(KeePass|KeePass2|Open Database File|Select key file manually|Plugins|Edit Group)" class="^(?!KeePass2)" instance="^(!?keepass2)"] floating enable
